Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有戀愛經驗的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這種事情一直很遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣的我 當看到她流下眼淚之時也發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮到底是在和什麼做鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼問我那種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會想說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水魔導師的攻擊變強大了 請求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有她哭泣的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新發現 現在準備開始探索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有帶傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為樟葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會和樟葉扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體都變涼了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗住民的體溫本來就是這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.38,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wanna fallin' LOVE.....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:32.05,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}予感--… 夢が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:37.90,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}約束しても　心がどこかで怯えてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ひとりじゃないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.75,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}信じたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:49.46,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思い続けてる だけで幸せなんて言えないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:55.26,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}虚ろな自信背負っていても　君が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:01.39,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}そして私の勇気になる 一つの言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.99,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君の世界を変えられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.52,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二つの恋が進化する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.74,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ホントだよ　巡らせた迷いが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.09,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}見つけた答えは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.97,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつでも君に導かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:22.50,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}届ける覚悟が 様にならなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.26,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}素直に伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.91,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ココロアルガママコエガキラメク
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.19,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Real come on voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:33.70,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響き渡るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:32.05,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}預感--… 夢想延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:37.90,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}儘管許下約定 心中某處依舊膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.00,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.75,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}明明想要這樣相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:49.46,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思念不斷滋生 但是卻無法說出幸福二字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:55.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}雖背負著虛無的自信 你依然嘴角上揚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:01.39,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的一句話就能成為我的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.99,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}若能改變你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.52,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就能進化成為兩份愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.74,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}真的哦 冥思苦想依舊迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.09,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}最終找到的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.97,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}無論何時都能引領著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:22.50,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就算沒有做好能夠傳達給你的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}大聲地說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.91,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}心靈深處的聲音熠熠生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:33.70,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響亮地傳達給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了點菜粥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(608,318)\3c&H000000&\fs29}Episode XI 蒼月下的…最終決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(664,288)\3c&H000000&\fs21}Blue moon·Ragnarok
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微坐起來一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界出現了歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為邪王真眼的力量也在減弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來燒還是沒退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也給我乖乖在家睡覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 都已經感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還勉強自己想到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就覺得頭暈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Vanishiment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了一晚已經得到完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 直到病好為止都不准你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你到底是想去哪裏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我不能回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前應該也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以闇炎之主的身份提問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問完之後也不打算責怪你什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很討厭這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花對我有所隱瞞而去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相很快就會昭然於天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 為什麼要撇下凸守我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這幅樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,de…death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還沒有死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會好了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那麼介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隨時都可以依靠邪王真眼的力量恢復健康
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道必須要服下盛開於邪王崖暗黑壁之巔的黑龍花才能痊癒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨意添加設定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站得那麼近小心被傳染啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.95,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是待得太久也有被傳染的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 奇美拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點恢復哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業堆了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛說出了禁言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了作業會皺眉頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 索菲婭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幾次想通過電子音信識別信號與她聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻從來沒得到她的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 到底怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙好像說她很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就能看出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮說了要開始戰爭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜到大概就會發展到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼丹谷生你是發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眼就發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子眼裏就只有你一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是十花姐告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這之後你打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能對那個孩子坐視不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那麼喜歡你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你突然這麼跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她甚至也從來沒有跟我說過那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然變得這麼正經了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生應該比較更瞭解戀愛這回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在迴避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有刻意迴避哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就別插手這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花那個時候也是 總是發生什麼立刻就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為看富堅你們很煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才來幫助你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒記得有拜託過你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的話你不要把人撞倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼但是什麼都有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:43.52,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是凸守嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在做什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心你就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要戰勝內在的自己 就需要波紋和魔法能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼輕易贊同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這個這次我也成功打敗敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得了最終勝利喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後 我就是魔法魔王少女改+α外傳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有種續篇繼續爛牌遊戲的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此以前的事以後已經全部被我遺棄到了無知的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統統消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮 這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天使的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會把她剛才的話當真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著「太好了 好像她沒事」之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 她只是在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事怎麼可能看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和七宮的交情也不是這一兩天的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你要我到底怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說戀情如夢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是夢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時間的流逝應該會慢慢地醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要強行叫醒她的話 反而會讓她覺得痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 這不關你事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實小森大人她最喜歡你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡小六花 小凸守還有富堅同學 小七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最喜歡中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都覺得羨慕她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是中二病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐你那麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我就能和大家分享同一種感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不是那麼容易就能變成中二病的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你開始憧憬的那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是一名堂堂正正的中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐你不是第二代邪王真眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亞 你好像處於迷茫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你已經取回你的記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃藥草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想著這樣比較容易對你傳達我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才特地換衣服過來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裙子可是很緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有箴言相贈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是魔法師 森夏的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏以前曾與冒名之人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(275,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且對他們降下了懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何面對自己體內的另一個自己並與之對戰的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個…自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 為了瞭解自己 應該將目光轉向外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我經由與冒牌貨的對戰 得以瞭解自己一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亞你也有不得不戰的對手才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去尋找那個對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時 你的前途將會一片光明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩啊 你懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 我幫你補充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好近啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆戰錘使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不僅對闇炎之主出手 還把魔爪伸向了冒牌森大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樟葉 月亮出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是漂亮的滿月哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說今晚是蒼月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼藍…之月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮喜歡我 但是我對六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂 太複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇炎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看看我的魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我尋找了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的對手果然只有勇者你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這樣做一個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王認證
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 六花不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才稍微不注意她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有蒼月對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 她已經注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是蒼藍之月的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼藍之月？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的記不得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗炎龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者你曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在自己體內的暗炎龍又會甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也希望它能被人喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自幾經風霜的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來永恆不變的絕對契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使超越時間 超越次元 前往平行世界的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也意欲繼續契約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以其絕對的力量出現在我面前的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾錯誤地降生到這個混沌不堪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其強大的封印之力以及其篡改記憶的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己真正的記憶正在逐漸被剝奪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾恐怕在不久的將來會化歸虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吾托付給汝 遙遠的汝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將寄宿我體內的暗炎龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它的身姿在這個世界現身的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬 改變 重鑄這個錯誤的世界的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活暗炎龍的鑰匙有三個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯庫爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:52.53,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}註：北歐神話中的諾恩三女神，是北歐神話中的命運女神。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有著與我共命運的力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集這三個鑰匙應該不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之永遠契約者啊 我將會等待那個時刻的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時步入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在終將到來的蒼藍之月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能將那力量交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是…隱藏的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然記得不太清楚 大概就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…有人挖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是邪王真眼放在這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是找過這裏的標記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是送往過去的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將鑰匙送往過去 只能使用平行世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張筆記裏提到的平行世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在第十四個鐵塔所指向的陰影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不知道那是從哪裏開始數的第十四個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了找到那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就這樣一點一滴地徹查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真相很快就會昭然於天下」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…一直為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模模糊糊地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的風景我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 無論何時都那麼認真地去中二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都那麼認真地去戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花 六花 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 這個就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明感冒了 還來找這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是惡化了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為必須由絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠的契約者來喚醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是勇太的永遠的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 必須找出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出來 將它作為證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事不用做也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是契約者 卻連一把鑰匙都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是索菲亞卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太是我的契約者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是你絕對的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在國中二年級的時候骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把它塞進那時的石膏裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我 居然還做了這麼麻煩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.75,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水與柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已的話 誰都看不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金屬上面刻字很麻煩 所以中途就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是很多年前放在這兒的東西 居然還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是塊石頭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是喚醒暗炎龍的魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼藍之月…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我查過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是蒼月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 拜託你了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠的契約者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧 現實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻開吧 神經突觸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanishment this world！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 格爾松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(441,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戰爭 讓我與你的暗炎龍一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應當與之一戰的對手 不可不戰的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是與勇者齊思 共求 同棄的暗炎龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我不可不戰的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我必須決出勝負的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是格爾松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞並重鑄世界一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法魔王少女 期望未來永恆獲得魔法的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓吾之暗炎龍的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深地烙印進你的雙目中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗炎龍根本不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然更不可能被看見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 六花的感冒復發倒床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 我要回溯時空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓現在變成7月8日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著崩潰狀態的作業 迎來了暑假的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業寫不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢葉長大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢葉也要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 我還是一次都沒去過她們希望我過去的雅加達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的作業沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於新生的索菲亞來說這不是什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宮在結束了與暗炎龍的戰鬥之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了向新的七宮的進化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 到底什麼地方改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會變的 未來永遠我都是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吾以不變之名 將郁集的東西破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保持不變從而需要參加使自己變得強大的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是連關定則嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 那就是連關定則哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也要找天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
